tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE asset_tokenization_processes (
  asset_token_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  asset_name VARCHAR(255),
  tokenization_date DATE,
  tokenization_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  tokenization_status VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE asset_tokens (
    token_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_name VARCHAR(255),
    asset_type VARCHAR(100),
    issuance_date DATE,
    total_supply INT
);

CREATE TABLE token_owners (
    owner_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    owner_name VARCHAR(255),
    ownership_percentage DECIMAL(5,2),
    FOREIGN KEY (token_id) REFERENCES asset_tokens(token_id)
);

CREATE TABLE asset_tokens (
    token_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_name VARCHAR(255),
    token_symbol VARCHAR(10),
    token_supply BIGINT,
    issuer_address VARCHAR(255),
    issuance_date TIMESTAMP,
    last_updated TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE token_holders (
    holder_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    holder_address VARCHAR(255),
    holding_amount BIGINT,
    holding_date TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY(token_id) REFERENCES asset_tokens(token_id)
);

CREATE TABLE token_transactions (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INT,
    sender_address VARCHAR(255),
    receiver_address VARCHAR(255),
    transaction_amount BIGINT,
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY(token_id) REFERENCES asset_tokens(token_id)
);

CREATE TABLE asset_tokens (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  token_id INT,
  asset_name VARCHAR(255),
  token_amount DECIMAL(18, 2),
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE token_owners (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  token_id INT,
  owner_address VARCHAR(255),
  ownership_percentage FLOAT,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE token_transactions (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  token_id INT,
  from_address VARCHAR(255),
  to_address VARCHAR(255),
  amount DECIMAL(18, 2),
  transaction_type VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE token_metadata (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  token_id INT,
  metadata_key VARCHAR(255),
  metadata_value TEXT,
  created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE asset_tokenization (
    asset_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    token_owner VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    token_amount INTEGER NOT NULL,
    token_creation_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE token_history (
    token_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    asset_id INTEGER REFERENCES asset_tokenization(asset_id),
    action_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    action_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    action_description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE token_transfers (
    transfer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INTEGER REFERENCES token_history(token_id),
    sender_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    receiver_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    transfer_amount INTEGER NOT NULL,
    transfer_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE token_ownership (
    ownership_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    token_id INTEGER REFERENCES token_transfers(token_id),
    new_owner_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    transfer_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE compliance_logs (
    log_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    action_performed VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    performed_by VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    log_description TEXT
);
